 \n      \"evidence\": \"CartService调用Redis的HGET操作延迟从1.5秒增至8.1秒（延迟倍数5.3倍），影响购物车相关操作\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"CartService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"前端调用CartService的AddItem操作延迟从5.2秒增至39.8秒（延迟倍数7.6倍），GetCart操作也有异常\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"ProductCatalogService\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"前端调用ProductCatalogService的GetProduct操作延迟从10秒增至11-20秒，存在轻微但持续的延迟\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现\n\n1. **最严重的延迟异常**：AdService的调用延迟增加了近10倍，这可能是根因候选\n2. **数据存储层问题**：Redis的HGET操作延迟显著增加，表明存储层可能存在性能问题\n3. **服务间调用链影响**：CartService的异常可能受到Redis延迟的影响\n4. **整体模式**：多个服务都出现响应时间增加，但AdService的异常最为突出\n\n建议进行更深入的分析来确定AdService延迟的根本原因，以及是否该问题引发了其他服务的级联故障。", "metric_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"client_error_ratio\",\n    \"error_ratio\",\n    \"pod_cpu_usage\",\n    \"rrt\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"node_memory_usage_rate\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Pod CPU usage increased from 0.01 to 0.6 (median_change_ratio: 1.9344), and rrt_max increased from 42946.0 to 190581.0 (median_change_ratio: 1.2644).\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage: 0.01 -> 0.6, rrt_max: 42946.0 -> 190581.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"Pod CPU usage increased from 0.0 to 0.6 (median_change_ratio: 2.0), and rrt_max increased from 42882.5 to 92829.0 (median_change_ratio: 0.7361).\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage: 0.0 -> 0.6, rrt_max: 42882.5 -> 92829.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"Pod CPU usage increased from 0.0 to 0.6 (median_change_ratio: 2.0), and rrt_max increased from 42730.0 to 93560.0 (median_change_ratio: 0.7459).\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage: 0.0 -> 0.6, rrt_max: 42730.0 -> 93560.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-05\",\n      \"reason\": \"Node memory usage rate decre